OL,3,CHouse prices in Wales rise for first
OL,4,Ctime in over a year
OL,6,FAverage house prices in these areas
OL,7,Fwere #250,921 and #281,382
OL,8,Frespectively - a new peak for Bridgend.
OL,10,FShaun Middleton, Head of Distribution
OL,11,Fat Principality Building Society,
OL,12,Fsaid: "This increase, bringing the
OL,13,Faverage price to #236,369 in Wales,
OL,14,Fmarks a significant turnaround and
OL,15,Fsuggests that the market may be
OL,16,Fstabilising.
