OL,3,CHouse prices in Wales rise for first
OL,4,Ctime in over a year
OL,6,F"The last few years have marked the
OL,7,Fmost challenging housing market
OL,8,Fconditions since the Global Financial
OL,9,FCrisis in 2008, with first-time buyers
OL,10,Fencountering the toughest conditions
OL,11,Fin about 70 years, according to the
OL,12,FBuilding Societies Association."
OL,14,FHe added that, with government
OL,15,Fcommitments to house building, the
OL,16,Fsociety expected to see house prices
OL,17,Fincrease with a higher volume of
OL,18,Ftransactions, "supported by better
OL,19,Feconomic conditions, increased
OL,20,Faffordability and growing buyer
OL,21,Finterest."
